Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.28,0:00:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother went through the trouble of getting me these tickets but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.62,0:00:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need three of them to participate in the drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.54,0:00:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you got forth place!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.48,0:00:14.39,alt,man,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.18,0:00:16.05,alt,other man,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.26,0:00:16.03,Default,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,I think I have one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.94,0:00:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, Aoi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Voila!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.84,0:00:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In case you win anything, I'll be taking half.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.15,0:00:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru, do you have anything coming up after our exams are over?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.88,0:00:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, right, there's something next week...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.89,0:00:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's the field trip with Tomoka and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.75,0:00:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.75,0:00:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just so happens to be during our break, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have a lot I wanted to teach them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.28,0:00:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They really learn well at that age.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.37,0:00:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to teach my students, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.18,0:01:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being the fifth-graders' coach, I can absolutely relate to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where are Tomoka and the others going for their field trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.51,0:01:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm not mistaken, they're going to Kyoto for two days.{Two days/XXX nights? --culex}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.55,0:01:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Kyoto, hm..?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.61,0:01:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.75,0:01:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've won the grand prize! You get a ticket to an autumn vacation in Kyoto for two!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.59,0:01:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.32,0:03:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.63,0:03:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Facial cream...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Carsickness medicine...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(315,473)}Nail clippers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.62,0:03:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(315,473)}Sewing kit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.64,0:03:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(315,473)}Stomach meds...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(315,473)}Eye meds...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(315,473)}Painkillers...{W/N: Holy shit, what is this, a drugstore?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.93,0:03:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(315,473)}Huh? What happened to my band-aids?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Argh, now I have to start over!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prez, this is the fifth time already...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're pumped for the trip with Sensei, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No-Not at all! It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just won by coincidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'd agreed to split the winnings...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prez, I honestly congratulate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.27,0:03:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us have perpared a little gift for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.57,0:03:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A gift? You shouldn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:03:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg of you, please accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just thanks for taking care of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Souno... Shouji... Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are these...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-P-P-PA-PA-PA-PA-PANTIES?!{I hope I didn't miscount here... --culex}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Success!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, gals! Are you prepared for the trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But of course. Rather than that, are {\i1}you{\i0} ready for the field trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I checked the luggage five times! It's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd have thought that Hasegawa-san and Aoi-san go to Kyoto the same day, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.23,0:04:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh~! This has to be fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.56,0:04:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fate", you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru said he'd meet us during free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh~! As long as I'm with Onii-chan, anywhere is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.06,0:05:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make tons of wonderful memories, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.56,0:05:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Mount Fuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.61,0:05:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, y-yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.50,0:05:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is red.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got a fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-D-D-D-Don't worry, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so? Well, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, what a piece of luck that I was be with you back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it wasn't for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I'd have lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Subaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.06,0:05:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're thinking so much about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of course, there's no one but you in my heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.44,0:06:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.03,0:06:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru, I...{TL explanation: I choose not to translate this quite common issue with "me too" and an abbreviated "to love" form or anything that'd sound awkward for two reasons: Primarily, we have context, and it makes her intent fairly obvious. Less importantly, watchers are quite frequently not deaf and will pick up on this oh-so-common pattern.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.25,0:06:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I went on a trip with another girl, her parents definitely wouldn't let us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.98,0:06:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since you're my childhood friend, yours trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.26,0:06:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't have gone with anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty much...{W/N: Come on, you could have gone for Chiho's "Desu yo ne~" here. Try harder, not even the Chihofags will want you to win at this rate.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.35,0:06:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we check out first?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should ask Tomoka and the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.89,0:06:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, it's nice with everyone, but I want to be alone with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?{W/N: COME ON! Get your standard lines right. It's "nandatte" if you're going to pull that joke!}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.51,0:06:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-san! Aoi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.19,0:06:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you both for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.35,0:06:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, where should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the Kiyomizu temple!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.79,0:06:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll jump off the stage!{[inaudible] --culex}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh~! I haven't done that yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.65,0:06:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! It's so high!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous, Maho-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, I'm gonna to fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No flying allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.48,0:07:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru, let's take a picture!{This translation is so boringly stock, it blows my mind. --culex}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is..?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.12,0:07:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They let you borrow costumes and backgrounds from the Genji story and take commemorative videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.59,0:07:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds great, fantastic! Let's do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suba... G-Genji-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.64,0:07:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomo... Murasaki no Ue...{arvon2: Please pay special attention to the following lines, Subaru/Tomoka are apparently speaking Classical Japanese and you should account for that. --culex}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.64,0:07:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Verily, ye look beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.36,0:08:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subarun! Nay, I mean, Genji-don!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,0:08:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'tis I, Yuugao!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari no Kimi, endly we meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, Genji no Kimi.{Normal}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.80,0:08:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan! I am your wife!{Normal, probably}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:29.59,note,,0000,0000,0000,,TL note: Pucelle is an archaic expression that refers to young, virgin women.{Often used in conjunction with Jeanne D'Arc. :: Who cares, probably even misleading. --culex}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magnificent! What splendid pucelles!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pucelles?! What the hell are you saying, Subaru?!{Normal Japanese again from here on out}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.52,0:08:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped, it says so right here in the script.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, you look pretty good in those clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.27,0:08:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You, too, Subaru... You look c—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.39,0:08:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-C-C-Cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.44,0:09:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru, you look cool! They totally fit you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.61,0:09:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the Hikaru Genji was someone as great as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.30,0:09:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh~! Onii-chan is a hottie!{Taking liberties with the TL here but should be fine.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.34,0:09:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, Hikaru Genji raised girls of the age of ten to his liking...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.27,0:09:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just have to stop here.{W/N: Disappointed Aoi is disappoint.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Youjiya..?{W/N: I don't like the title "I have few friends".}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Children's house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.23,0:09:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shubaru-san, I'm a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Child! I'm a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.24,0:09:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me three!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, I'm a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.54,0:09:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who should I pick?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:10:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru! No! Stop! Not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.02,0:10:04.56,note,,0000,0000,0000,,TL note: 幼児 (Youji) means "child",\Nbut the homophone 楊枝 means "toothpick". This is a pun, laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.57,0:10:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Dad's in Hawaii and he wanted me to send him some toothpicks...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.05,0:10:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.74,0:10:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd have thought we'd be staying in the same hotel...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys here as well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.91,0:10:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing more than coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of doubt that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.65,0:10:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hotel's fully booked, so I guess we'll have to live with one room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, we're on a couple's trip, so a double room is to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.45,0:11:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.13,0:11:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.42,0:11:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and take a shower first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to get in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:15.65,Default,boy,0000,0000,0000,,Takenaka, let's check out the hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:14.14,alt,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you dropped this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.14,0:11:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takenaka, what's holding you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-S-Shower..?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been walking all day and got pretty sweaty, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.58,0:12:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get some drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-P-P-P-P—{Timer's note: [stutters externally]}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do with these..?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wear them and win!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.20,0:13:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no! No way! Too embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.62,0:13:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!{E/N: "Tadaima" says the elephant and the trunk extends.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to do..?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do with these panties?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't fall asleep here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You had trouble sleeping, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Too many things going through my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, "Too"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.23,0:13:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, I see, you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were worried, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.65,0:13:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.57,0:13:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Return the panties you took last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, you look scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Good morning, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We kept waiting for you to play with us in our room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.64,0:14:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to come over tonight, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.47,0:14:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what was that supposed to mean? Explain yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.73,0:14:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You picked up Maho's panties last night. Tonight, you're going to return them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How exactly do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, why do you know they're Maho's?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Su~barun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw Maho drop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.04,0:14:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why the hell didn't you return them right then and there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to! But a friend called me and I had to hide them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did you make {\i1}me{\i0} take those panties up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been through this already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.59,0:15:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You asshole!{E/N: Yes, I know, the fans will cry about this, but just look at the background. It's red. Subaru is shouting at the top of his lungs. There's absolutely no way a native English speaker wouldn't call someone an "asshole" right about now.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you hid them in your shirt, you lost the right to lecture me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you out! Tonight, we're returning Maho's panties!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.04,0:15:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm{\i0} the one helping {\i1}you{\i0}! You picked them up in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.85,0:15:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading out for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, the girls are in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.89,0:15:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take this opportunity to sneak into their room and put them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.49,0:15:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miho-nee?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.15,0:15:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watano-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Planning to peek into the baths?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.46,0:15:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.84,0:16:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking about basketball practice and stuff, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.93,0:16:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You basketball fanatics sure never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.82,0:16:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah well, better than doing dirty things to Aoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.91,0:16:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru's a safe person like me, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What part of you is safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought lots of things to play with you, Mihoshi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have fun together nice and slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Subaru, if I ever become a murderer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave my sister in your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Miho-nee.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.75,0:16:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just wasted a lot of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.84,0:16:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you even have her panties?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.59,0:16:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.12,0:16:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The panties!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, you moron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.02,0:17:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.71,0:17:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.17,0:17:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girls' bath is over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.67,0:17:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The water feels good...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we were walking around a lot, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Hot springs, hot springs, outdoors!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.31,0:17:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.30,0:17:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Don't peek, definitely don't peek, I won't forgive you if you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.35,0:17:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But just where did my panties go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:17:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Natsuhi took them like he did a while ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:18:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What nonsense are you on about? Maho must've dropped them somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.85,0:18:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The field trip's over tomorrow, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.54,0:18:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These two days sure went by at lightning speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.31,0:18:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.29,0:18:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru's going to play with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.88,0:18:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make even more great memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.13,0:18:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh~! I want to make memories with Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.53,0:18:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-san... I wonder what you're doing right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little bit further...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.75,0:18:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One way or another, I retrieved them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.87,0:18:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We wasted so much time... They're back already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped. We'll go play with them in their room, find an opening and return the panties.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will this improvised plan even work?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Natsuhi's here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not here because I want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.73,0:19:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you doing?! We're not here for a pillow fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.14,0:19:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.29,0:19:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll create an opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't put up with it anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A battle is a battle. We won't let you off the hook so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh~! Don't be shy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.93,0:19:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hasegawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.38,0:19:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A floater!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A no-look pass?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru-san, nice shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.01,0:20:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh~! That was cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is a pillow fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really do love basketball, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.26,0:20:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.78,0:20:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ao...i?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.12,0:20:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Prez, how was our gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, you won, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.50,0:20:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You feel like dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he's got the wrong idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:21:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must think I usually wear something this perverted...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.12,0:21:05.94,Default,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,I prepared myself so much, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:06.38,alt,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:11.04,Default,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to try them on, nothing more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.89,0:21:11.66,alt,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry! Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.36,0:21:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die, Prez! Wasn't that a huge success?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.82,0:21:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back! Earth to Aoi!{Again, taking liberties here, but should be fine}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.54,0:21:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoi, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.65,0:21:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A present for you because you coach the fifth-grade team.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I really have this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.85,0:21:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Thanks a lot for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.66,0:21:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.80,0:21:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it just can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.51,0:23:49.53,note,,0000,0000,0000,,(This seems to be an OVA/recap episode coming up, we won't release subs for that.\NBy the way, we're recruiting typesetters.)
